statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_reports;
SELECT website_id, traffic_date, page_views FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE website_id = 1;
SELECT conversion_rate, unique_visitors FROM website_traffic_reports ORDER BY unique_visitors DESC;
SELECT website_id, page_views FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE page_views > 1000;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE conversion_rate BETWEEN 0.2 AND 0.5;
SELECT website_id, traffic_date, page_views, unique_visitors, conversion_rate FROM website_traffic_reports ORDER BY website_id ASC, traffic_date DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT website_id, page_views, unique_visitors FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY unique_visitors DESC, page_views ASC
SELECT website_id, traffic_date, page_views FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE traffic_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' AND unique_visitors > 100 ORDER BY traffic_date DESC
SELECT website_id, page_views, unique_visitors, conversion_rate FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE page_views >= 1000 AND conversion_rate < 0.2 ORDER BY conversion_rate ASC, page_views DESC
SELECT AVG(page_views) AS avg_page_views, MAX(unique_visitors) AS max_unique_visitors, MIN(conversion_rate) AS min_conversion_rate FROM website_traffic_reports
SELECT * FROM website_traffic LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, date, visitor_id FROM website_traffic WHERE date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY visits DESC;
SELECT id, date, conversion_rate, page_conversion FROM conversion_rates WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT source_page, destination_page, conversion_rate FROM conversion_rates WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_visited, visitor_id FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited = 'Home' ORDER BY visitor_id DESC;
SELECT date, conversion_rate, page_conversion FROM conversion_rates WHERE destination_page = 'Thank You Page' ORDER BY date ASC, conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT page_visited, visitor_id FROM website_traffic WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' AND visitor_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT source_page, destination_page, conversion_rate FROM conversion_rates WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' AND date <= '2022-01-15' ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC, source_page ASC;

SELECT page_url, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 123
SELECT page_url, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_url
SELECT * FROM conversion_rates WHERE conversion_type = 'purchase'
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS conversion_count FROM conversion_rates GROUP BY visitor_id
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 123;
SELECT page_url, visit_timestamp, referral_source FROM website_traffic WHERE referral_source = 'Google';

SELECT page_url, COUNT(*) AS total_conversions FROM conversion_rates GROUP BY page_url;
SELECT website_traffic.page_url, performance_analysis.conversion_event FROM website_traffic JOIN performance_analysis ON website_traffic.visitor_id = performance_analysis.visitor_id;
SELECT * FROM WebsiteVisits;
SELECT visitor_ip, page_visited, visit_date FROM WebsiteVisits WHERE conversion_status = TRUE;
SELECT page_id, page_url, page_title FROM PageViews ORDER BY average_time_spent DESC;
SELECT visitor_ip, conversion_date FROM ConversionRates WHERE conversion_status = FALSE ORDER BY conversion_date ASC;
SELECT source_name, source_type, daily_visits_count, conversion_rate FROM TrafficSources WHERE daily_visits_count > 1000;
SELECT * FROM WebsiteVisits WHERE visit_date = '2022-01-01' AND conversion_status = true;
SELECT visitor_ip, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM WebsiteVisits GROUP BY visitor_ip ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT page_url, page_title, average_time_spent FROM PageViews WHERE unique_visitors_count > 100 ORDER BY average_time_spent DESC;

SELECT source_name, source_type, daily_visits_count, conversion_rate FROM TrafficSources WHERE conversion_rate > 0.1 ORDER BY daily_visits_count DESC, conversion_rate DESC;
